5
00:02:38,032 --> 00:03:01,423
Udang Saranang Gacami Dhamang Saranang Gacami Sanggang Saranang Gacami Duthi Ampi Udang Saranang Gacami

6
00:03:02,247 --> 00:03:30,347
Duthi Ampi Dhammam Saranam Gacchami Duthi Ampi Sangam Saranam Gacchami Thati Ampi Budham Saranam Gacchami Thati Ampi Dhammam Saranam Gacchami

7
00:03:31,187 --> 00:03:58,106
