11
00:04:25,711 --> 00:04:31,562
Vairamani Sikapadam Samadhi Amin.

12
00:04:33,485 --> 00:04:41,442
Vida me silam agapalanyanasa pachayohotu.

13
00:04:42,281 --> 00:05:10,028
Iti piso bhagavah arahamsammasambuddho vijjacharanasampanno sugato lokavidhu anuttaro purisadhammasarati satta-deva-manusanamputtobhagavati

14
00:05:10,733 --> 00:05:39,305
ye ca buddha-aditha ca ye ca buddha-anagadha pachupanna ca ye buddha-aham vandami-sabhadha nati me saranam anyam buddho me saranam varam etena sacca vajena hotu me jaya-mangalam

15
00:05:40,129 --> 00:06:02,492
Kāye na vāca-cittay na pā-māde na māyā-kathāṃ Ācchayāṃ kāma-mibhante bhūrī-paññā tathā-gathā Svakāto bhagavata-dhammo sāndhitiko akaliko

16
00:06:03,079 --> 00:06:26,050
Ehi Pasiko Opanayiko Pachatam Veditabo Vinyuhiti Yechadama Atitacha Yechadama Anagatha Pachupanachaya Dhamma Aham Vandami Sabadam

17
00:06:26,754 --> 00:06:55,192
nāti me sāraṇaṁ anyāṁ tamo me sāraṇaṁ varāṁ ete na sācchā vācchē na hūtu me jāya-maṅgalāṁ kāye na vācchā cittē na pāma de na māyā kathāṁ acchā yāṅ kāma me dhammā sāndhitika akalika

18
00:06:55,459 --> 00:07:16,540
Supatipanno bhagavato savakasangho Pujupatipanno bhagavato savakasangho Nyayapatipanno bhagavato savakasangho

19
00:07:16,738 --> 00:07:33,819
Samicchipatipanno bhagavato savakasangho Yadidhanjatari purisayugani attapurisapukala

20
00:07:34,357 --> 00:08:03,047
Hei sa bhagavato sa vakasangho Pahuneyo pahuneyo Dakineyo anjali karaneyo Anuttaran punaketam lukasati Ye ca sangha adhita ca Ye ca sangha anagata

21
00:08:03,685 --> 00:08:31,767
Pachupanna Chayi Sangha Aham Vandami Sabadam Gnatime Saranam Ganyam Sangome Saranam Varam Etena Satya Vachena Hotume Jaya Mangalam Kayena Vachachitena Pamatena Mayakatam

22
00:08:32,254 --> 00:08:56,490
Acheyankamamesangapunyaketamanuptaran Anekajatisansaransandawisanmanibisan Gahakerakamgawesantudukajatipunapunam

23
00:08:57,027 --> 00:09:19,322
Gahakarakadithauzipunagehanakahazi Sabatebhasukabagakahakuthamvisankatam Visankarakatanchitamthananamkayamachakam

24
00:09:20,601 --> 00:09:48,785
Awija Pacha Sankara Sankara Pacha Vinyana Vinyana Pacha Nama Rupa Nama Rupa Pacha Salayatana Salayatana Pacha Paso Pasa Pacha Vedana Vedana Pacha Tangha Tangha Pacha Upadana

25
00:09:49,457 --> 00:10:17,304
Upadana Pachabhava Upavapachajati Jati Pachaya Jara Maranan Soka Parideva Dukkha Domina Supaya Sasambhavanti Deva Mitasa Kevalasa Dukkha Kandasa Samudaya Hoti

26
00:10:17,892 --> 00:10:44,658
avijjaya tveva asesa viraga niroda sankara nirodo sankara niroda vijnana nirodo vijnana niroda nama rupa nirodo nama rupa niroda salayatna nirodo

27
00:10:45,212 --> 00:11:12,537
salayatana niroda, pasa nirodo pasa niroda, vedana nirodo vedana niroda, tanda nirodo tanda niroda, upadana nirodo upadana niroda, bhava nirodo

28
00:11:12,971 --> 00:11:40,043
Bhava Nirodha Jati Nirodo Jati Nirodha Jara Maranam Soka Hari Deva Dukha Domina Supayasa Nirojanti Ewa Vittasa Kevalasa Dukha Kandasa Nirodo Hoti

29
00:11:40,528 --> 00:12:09,557
Sabe sankarani jati yadapanya yapasati Adhani bindati duke esamago vissudhya Sabe sankarani jati yadapanya yapasati Adhani bindati duke esamago vissudhya

30
00:12:10,211 --> 00:12:38,447
Sabbe dhamma anattati adhapanya yappasati Atthani bhindati duke esamago vissudhiyam Anicca vattasankara upadhavaya dhammino Upajitvanirujanti tesang upasamosukho

31
00:12:39,187 --> 00:13:07,152
Dukkha Vata Sankara Upadavaya Damino Upajitva Nirujanti Tesam Upasamo Sukho Anatta Vata Sankara Upadavaya Damino Upajitva Nirujanti Tesam Upasamo Sukho

32
00:13:09,510 --> 00:13:13,837
So we can bring to mind anyone we know is having a hard time.

33
00:13:13,857 --> 00:13:36,075
And at this moment, there are people who are suffering from a physical or mental disease.

34
00:13:39,058 --> 00:13:46,467
There are people in the process of dying and those who have died and left grieving family, relatives and friends.

35
00:13:50,232 --> 00:13:53,797
And there are people going hungry, homeless and destitute.

36
00:13:57,380 --> 00:14:01,466
There are those struggling with personal or interpersonal difficulties.

37
00:14:05,571 --> 00:14:07,833
All the victims of prejudices,

38
00:14:11,307 --> 00:14:17,774
All those caught up in wars and repressive regimes and those being tortured.

39
00:14:21,739 --> 00:14:25,903
All those suffering from natural disasters and climate crisis.

40
00:14:30,389 --> 00:14:35,796
All the sentient beings are being cruelly treated and unnecessarily slaughtered.

41
00:14:39,606 --> 00:14:45,354
and all who find life meaningless.

42
00:14:45,374 --> 00:15:09,562
Karaniyam ratakusalena yantam santam padam abhisame ca sakoju ca suju ca suvajo ca samudu anaptimani santu sakoja subharu ca

43
00:15:10,032 --> 00:15:39,684
Apakichocha salahu kauti Santindriyocha nipakocha Apagabokule suvananukido Nacchakudamsamachare kenshi Yena vinyupare upavadeyom Sukhino vakemino hontu

44
00:15:39,799 --> 00:16:03,697
Sābe sātā bāvantu sukhi tathā Ye kecchī pāna-bhūtati Tāsa vāta-vāra-vāāna-vāseṣa Dīgāvā ye vāntava Majjhima-rasa-kanukatulā

45
00:16:04,488 --> 00:16:31,203
Dītāvā yevā adhītā yecchādure vāsānti āvidhūre Bhūtāvā sambhāveṣīvā sābe satāvā vāntu sukhi tathā Nāparo parambhikubheta nātimanyetā kathā cīnā kīcchī

46
00:16:31,690 --> 00:16:39,538
Byalosana bhakti-kasanya, Nanyamanya sadhukam itchaya.

47
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:48,249
Mata yata niyamputta, Ayusahekamputtambanurake.

48
00:16:49,331 --> 00:16:57,360
Pevampi sababutesu, Manasambhavaye aparimana.

49
00:16:58,133 --> 00:17:24,663
Netencha Sabalokasmi Manasambhavaye Aparimanam Udamadocha Thiriyamcha Asambhadam Maweram Asambhadam Thitancharam Nisinova Sayanova Yavatasa Vigatamido

50
00:17:25,436 --> 00:17:54,414
etam satimna dhiteya brahma-metam viharam itamadhu dhiting ca anupagamah silavah dasanena sampanam kameh suvinayakedham nahijatukabhasayam punaretiti

51
00:17:56,722 --> 00:18:09,788
Our resolutions for the day, something we want to do, something we don't want to do.

52
00:18:18,491 --> 00:18:41,007
Ima ya dhamma lu dhamma pati pati ya buddham puje mi Ima ya dhamma lu dhamma pati pati ya buddham puje mi

53
00:18:46,301 --> 00:18:55,688
